          ř     Kickin' fido-style mail net!
           ř     Spans half the globe!
            ř     Easy to set up :)
             ř     Nice & friendly atmosphere!
              ř     Regions, Hubs, Nodes & Points available!
               ř     Technical help available on ANY subject!
                ř     D/L this & Join Soon!

 .------------------.
 |  FluffyNet Info  |
 `------------------'

   @{b}Fluffy Net@{ub} was a joint creation by Niki Murkett (Redrum BBS)
   & Roger Wilco (Cyberzone BBS) to be a simple echo network
   for happy people. :)

   Please encourage other people to join up, and please write as
   many messages everyday as you can.

   Any of the BBS's in the current @{"nodelist" link list} will be able to help
   you set up Fluffy Net.

   Home of Fluffy Net is Total Eclipse (formerly Dave's Place/Redrum BBS).

 .------------------.
 |  Standard Echos  |
 `------------------'

 FN-GEN          General chat
 FN-SYSOP        SysOps Only chat
 FN-AV           Audio/Visual chat (Music, graphics, videos etc)
 FN-ESP          Paranoramal/UFO chat
 FN-HELP         Help on Any subject
 FN-NET          Internet chat (Web pages to visit, etc)
 FN-ELEC         Electronics chat, Amature radio, etc
 FN-CODE         Programmers chat
 FN-MAXS         MAX's help and support echo (and file echo)

@endnode
